.com/us-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/another-victory-for-aipac-wesley-bell-and-8-5-million-defeat-squad-member-cori-bush/00000191-2adb-d2a9-a5dd-3edb30180001</guid></item><item><title>西方大国越来越担心俄罗斯与伊朗的合作不断发展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/western-powers-increasingly-concerned-about-growing-russia-iran-cooperation/00000191-2911-d642-a9d5-bb51462b0000</link><description>在有报道称俄罗斯正在向伊朗提供军事援助并试图向胡塞武装提供武器后，西方外交官发出了警报。一位外交官告诉《国土报》，“俄罗斯的介入让我们非常担心，以色列也应该担心”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/western-powers-increasingly-concerned-about-growing-russia-iran-cooperation/00000191-2911-d642-a9d5-bb51462b0000</guid></item><item><title>对于真主党来说，以色列痛苦的等待是其报复的一部分，但它仍然希望避免战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/for-hezbollah-israels-agonizing-wait-is-part-of-its-revenge/00000191-2950-d642-a9d5-bb50d8a50000</link><description>哈桑·纳斯鲁拉周二在贝鲁特发表了激烈的演讲，但没有明确威胁爆发地区战争——他的组织及其伊朗赞助人显然仍在寻求避免这种情况</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/for-hezbollah-israels-agonizing-wait-is-part-of-its-revenge/00000191-2950-d642-a9d5-bb50d8a50000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯：美国已表示无需将冲突升级至伊朗和以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article-live/nasrallah-nerve-racking-anticipation-part-of-hezbollah-response-goal-to-exhaust-israel/00000191-2a95-dcd6-abf7-7e975efc0000</link><description>戈兰地区委员会：以色列北部居民必须留在避难所附近，并尽量减少不必要的旅行 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部表示，自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 39,653 名巴勒斯坦人在加沙丧生 ■ 真主党声称对以色列北部的无人机袭击负责 ■ 以色列国防军，辛贝特称以色列战斗机袭击了黎巴嫩南部真主党军事基地</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 02:12:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article-live/nasrallah-nerve-racking-anticipation-part-of-hezbollah-response-goal-to-exhaust-israel/00000191-2a95-dcd6-abf7-7e975efc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长告诉内塔尼亚胡：你的内阁工作程序有缺陷，损害公共利益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-tells-netanyahu-your-cabinets-work-procedures-are-flawed-harm-the-public/00000191-293d-d1b4-a399-7dbf1ec20000</link><description>加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉（Gali Baharav-Miara）在给总理的信中表示，内阁秘书发布的法律意见超越了他的职权，“在安全领域产生了严重影响”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 22:17:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-tells-netanyahu-your-cabinets-work-procedures-are-flawed-harm-the-public/00000191-293d-d1b4-a399-7dbf1ec20000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫官员拒绝赎罪日户外祈祷请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-official-rejects-requests-for-yom-kippur-outdoor-prayer/00000191-28b0-d1b4-a399-7cb67ef60000</link><description>在居民和政界人士的强烈抗议之后，市政府发表了一份似乎与自己的裁决相矛盾的声明</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:54:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-official-rejects-requests-for-yom-kippur-outdoor-prayer/00000191-28b0-d1b4-a399-7cb67ef60000</guid></item><item><title>美国-以色列摔跤手阿米特·埃洛尔在巴黎奥运会上夺得金牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/american-israeli-wrestler-amir-elor-strikes-gold-at-paris-olympics/00000191-2975-dcd6-abf7-7f77c7700000</link><description>这位 20 岁的父母出生于以色列外籍人士，成为在奥运会上赢得金牌的最年轻的美国摔跤手（无论男女）</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/american-israeli-wrestler-amir-elor-strikes-gold-at-paris-olympics/00000191-2975-dcd6-abf7-7f77c7700000</guid></item><item><title>伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚被杀后，哈马斯任命加沙领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔为酋长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-names-gaza-leader-yahya-sinwar-as-chief-following-ismail-haniyeh-killing/00000191-290f-dcda-adf3-6d4f5a180000</link><description>辛瓦尔曾担任加沙哈马斯领导人，也是10月7日事件的策划者，现在将担任该组织的最高政治领导人。这一任命被视为哈马斯向以色列、美国、人质协议调解人和巴勒斯坦公众发出的信息</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 20:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-names-gaza-leader-yahya-sinwar-as-chief-following-ismail-haniyeh-killing/00000191-290f-dcda-adf3-6d4f5a180000</guid></item><item><title>涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦囚犯的士兵在测谎仪测试中撒谎；检方将逮捕期限延长至周日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-palestinian-prisoner-lied-on-polygraph-test/00000191-2868-d5e8-a397-fef831300000</link><description>这些士兵涉嫌情节严重的虐待行为、强奸情况下的鸡奸行为、侵犯权力和不当行为</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 19:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-palestinian-prisoner-lied-on-polygraph-test/00000191-2868-d5e8-a397-fef831300000</guid></item><item><title>英国廉价航空公司 EasyJet 暂停以色列航班直至 2025 年春季</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/budget-u-k-airline-easyjet-suspends-israel-flights-until-spring-2025/00000191-28ee-d2a9-a5dd-3eff6e320000</link><description>由于担心与伊朗和真主党发生重大冲突，易捷航空 (EasyJet) 在取消和暂停往返以色列航班的众多航空公司中名列前茅。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:52:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/budget-u-k-airline-easyjet-suspends-israel-flights-until-spring-2025/00000191-28ee-d2a9-a5dd-3eff6e320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称，被认为失踪的比尔哈·伊农 (Bilha Inon) 于 10 月 7 日被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-bilha-inon-considered-missing-was-killed-on-october-7/00000191-28de-d642-a9d5-bbdefeb30000</link><description>据军方称，在她家附近发现的证据证实她是被谋杀的。伊农的家人于10月7日宣布了她被谋杀的消息，第二天开始哀悼她和她的丈夫雅科维</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:50:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-bilha-inon-considered-missing-was-killed-on-october-7/00000191-28de-d642-a9d5-bbdefeb30000</guid></item><item><title>华尔兹谈夏皮罗：美国准备好迎接一位犹太副总统了吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-06/ty-article/.highlight/walz-over-shapiro-will-america-ever-be-ready-for-a-jewish-vp/00000191-2838-d5e8-a397-fef8de350000</link><description>副总统卡马拉·哈里斯选择明尼苏达州州长蒂姆·沃尔兹作为她的竞选伙伴，而不是宾夕法尼亚州州长乔什·夏皮罗。无论沃尔兹的资历如何，最近发生的事件都会给许多美国犹太人留下苦涩的味道</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:39:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-06/ty-article/.highlight/walz-over-shapiro-will-america-ever-be-ready-for-a-jewish-vp/00000191-2838-d5e8-a397-fef8de350000</guid></item><item><title>性别中立的酸奶标志引发以色列网络文化战争风暴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/gender-neutral-yogurt-logo-sparks-israeli-internet-culture-war-firestorm/00000191-2874-d102-a39d-3c7467840000</link><description>以色列食品巨头施特劳斯为其广受欢迎的儿童酸奶杯“Dwarfs”推出了新标志，因此这个最初以男性形式书写的单词现在可以读作女性或男性。社交媒体上几乎立即爆发了对这一变化的强烈反对，许多用户呼吁抵制</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 17:39:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/gender-neutral-yogurt-logo-sparks-israeli-internet-culture-war-firestorm/00000191-2874-d102-a39d-3c7467840000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第305天：真主党主席表示伊朗不应该参与公开战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-305-iran-shouldnt-be-part-of-open-war-hezbollah-chief-says/00000191-2859-d2a9-a5dd-3e59bdec0000</link><description>真主党火箭弹和无人机对以色列北部的袭击造成三人受伤 ■ 戈兰和上加利利地区议会指示居民留在避难所附近 ■ 据报道，普京要求伊朗最高领导人在德黑兰对哈尼亚杀戮的回应中避免针对以色列平民 ■ 八名巴勒斯坦人丧生，其中包括四名青少年，在以色列国防军突袭、空袭约旦河西岸期间，巴勒斯坦官员表示 ■ 这是战争开始 305 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 16:22:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-305-iran-shouldnt-be-part-of-open-war-hezbollah-chief-says/00000191-2859-d2a9-a5dd-3e59bdec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正统派极端分子在招募中心的战斗中失败，但他们正在赢得战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/haredi-extremists-lost-the-battle-at-the-recruitment-center-but-theyre-winning-the-war/00000191-2837-d5e8-a397-feff9d4e0000</link><description>通过资金充足、复杂且有时甚至是暴力的运动，强硬的正统派活动人士成功地减缓了将该社区融入以色列军队的努力。克服它们需要新的决心</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 15:58:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/haredi-extremists-lost-the-battle-at-the-recruitment-center-but-theyre-winning-the-war/00000191-2837-d5e8-a397-feff9d4e0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党向以色列北部开火，造成一人重伤；以色列国防军：拦截弹可能击中平民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/19-wounded-by-hezbollah-fire-to-israels-north-idf-interceptor-may-have-hit-civilians/00000191-2812-dcd6-abf7-7e170da60000</link><description>军方正在调查为何拦截弹是从黎巴嫩发射的火箭发射的，但在未击中目标后未能在空中爆炸。周二早些时候，真主党附属组织 Al-Hadath 报道称，以色列国防军无人机袭击造成黎巴嫩南部 5 人死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 15:45:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/19-wounded-by-hezbollah-fire-to-israels-north-idf-interceptor-may-have-hit-civilians/00000191-2812-dcd6-abf7-7e170da60000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼以色列说唱歌手分享未向媒体公开的警察录像</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-rapper-shares-police-footage-not-released-to-the-media/00000191-27ab-ddbb-a7fd-affbf8a10000</link><description>视频显示，警察从海法的反战抗议者手中扯下巴勒斯坦旗帜。 《国土报》的镜头显示一名警察摄影师拍摄了后来在说唱歌手的 Telegram 频道上分享的内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 15:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-rapper-shares-police-footage-not-released-to-the-media/00000191-27ab-ddbb-a7fd-affbf8a10000</guid></item><item><title>在伊朗请求军事援助后，普京要求伊朗避免以色列平民伤亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-08-06/ty-article/putin-asks-iran-to-avoid-israeli-civilian-casualties-after-iran-requests-military-aid/00000191-27f3-dbbc-ab95-37f371760000</link><description>一个俄罗斯代表团前往德黑兰，试图说服伊朗不要在对以色列的报复中针对平民，以防止大规模战争。 《纽约时报》报道称，伊朗要求提供先进的防空系统，消息人士称俄罗斯正在交付这些系统</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:45:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-08-06/ty-article/putin-asks-iran-to-avoid-israeli-civilian-casualties-after-iran-requests-military-aid/00000191-27f3-dbbc-ab95-37f371760000</guid></item></channel></rss>